OL,3,CMan arrested in connection with theft
OL,4,Cof 22 tonnes of cheese
OL,6,FDetectives investigating the theft of
OL,7,Fmore than 22 tonnes of cheese, some of
OL,8,Fwhich was made in Somerset, have
OL,9,Farrested a 63-year-old man on
OL,10,Fsuspicion of fraud and handling stolen
OL,11,Fgoods.
OL,13,FA Metropolitan Police spokesman said:
OL,14,F"On Monday October 21, police received
OL,15,Fa report of the theft of a large
OL,16,Fquantity of cheese from a manufacturer
OL,17,Fbased in Southwark.
