OL,3,CMan arrested in connection with theft
OL,4,Cof 22 tonnes of cheese
OL,6,F"Investigating officers have since
OL,7,Farrested a 63-year-old man on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of fraud by false
OL,9,Frepresentation and handling Stolen
OL,10,FGoods.
OL,12,F"The man was taken to a south London
OL,13,Fpolice station where he was
OL,14,Fquestioned. He has since been bailed
OL,15,Fpending further inquiries. Inquiries
OL,16,Fremain ongoing."
OL,18,FThe cheese was taken from Neal's Yard,
OL,19,Fa British, London-based, artisan
OL,20,Fcheese retailer and distributor.
