OL,4,Cof 22 tonnes of cheese
OL,6,FIt said it delivered more than 950
OL,7,Fwheels of cheddar to the alleged
OL,8,Ffraudster posing as a wholesale
OL,9,Fdistributor for a major French
OL,10,Fretailer before realising what had
OL,11,Fhappened.
OL,13,FThe company said it still paid Hafod,
OL,14,FWestcombe and Pitchfork, the producers
OL,15,Fof the cheese, so they would not have
OL,16,Fto bear the cost "despite the
OL,17,Fsignificant financial blow".
