OL,3,CMan arrested in connection with theft
OL,4,Cof 22 tonnes of cheese
OL,6,FMr Calver, 42, said: "I was really
OL,7,Fconcerned about what it was and the
OL,8,Fimplications of it.
OL,10,F"Neal's Yard have been fantastic. We
OL,11,Fare just trying to support them as
OL,12,Fmuch as possible by encouraging people
OL,13,Fto shop with them.
OL,15,F"It is a huge, very difficult loss."
OL,17,FNeal's Yard said it was working with
OL,18,Fpolice to identify the perpetrators.
