OL,3,CMan arrested in connection with theft
OL,4,Cof 22 tonnes of cheese
OL,6,FMr Calver said it took him half a day
OL,7,Fto sell one cheese at a market this
OL,8,Fweekend.
OL,10,F"It is ridiculous ` out of all the
OL,11,Fthings to steal in the world ` 22
OL,12,Ftonnes of cheese?" he added.
OL,14,F"What it does show, which I am amazed
OL,15,Fabout, is the value people put on
OL,16,Fthese amazing artisan foods."
OL,18,FCelebrity chef Jamie Oliver asked his
OL,19,Ffollowers on social media to be alert
OL,20,Ffor "lorryloads of posh cheese" being
OL,21,Fsold "for cheap".
