OL,4,Cof 22 tonnes of cheese
OL,6,FHe told his 10.5 million followers:
OL,7,F"There has been a great cheese
OL,8,Frobbery. Some of the best cheddar
OL,9,Fcheese in the world has been stolen."
OL,11,FOliver described it as a "real shame",
OL,12,Fadding: "If anyone hears anything
OL,13,Fabout posh cheese going for cheap,
OL,14,Fit's probably some wrong'uns.
OL,16,F"Are they going to unpeel it from the
OL,17,Fcloth, and cut it and grate it and get
OL,18,Frid of it in the fast food industry,
OL,19,Fin the commercial industry? I don't
OL,20,Fknow ` it feels like a really weird
OL,21,Fthing to nick."
