OL,3,CMan arrested in connection with theft
OL,4,Cof 22 tonnes of cheese
OL,6,FMr Calver's Westcombe Cheddar is aged
OL,7,Ffor 12 to 18 months and he said the
OL,8,Fstolen cheese was produced 15 months
OL,9,Fago.
OL,11,FHe said: "What worries me is the trust
OL,12,Felement in things. At the end of the
OL,13,Fday, what we need to have is more
OL,14,Ftrust in the food supply system,
OL,15,Frather than less of it.
OL,17,F"I hope more people will want to know
OL,18,Fwhere their food comes from."
OL,20,FMr Calver's cheddar sells for #7 for
OL,21,F250g.
